"content": "<p>A bird used, along with doves, for sacrifices, especially by those who could not afford lambs.</p>\n<h2>A pigeon offered as sacrifice</h2>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Lev1:14\">LEV 1:14</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Gen15:9\">GEN 15:9</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Lev1:15-Lev1:17\">LEV 1:15–1:17</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Lev14:21-Lev14:22\">LEV 14:21–14:22</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Lev15:14\">LEV 15:14</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Lev15:29\">LEV 15:29</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Num6:10\">NUM 6:10</a></p>\n<h2>Pigeons offered as a sacrifice by the poor</h2>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Lev5:7\">LEV 5:7</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Luke2:22-Luke2:24\">LUK 2:22–2:24</a></p>",
